LINE.Text: Relative caregivers are an essential part of providing safe, stable and loving homes for
thousands of children in L.A. County. But these children get the shortest end of the stick
when it comes to support and resources.
Children placed with relatives have better outcomes, including fewer behavioral problems,
higher high school graduation rates and less chance of unemployment and homelessness
